{"tid":674384,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(又買英幼齒)慕遜加柏吼實紅軍小將 利記取消友賽安排","createTime":"2018-05-22T15:38:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T15:52:23.000Z","uid":37218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"796703bb852586f4385486e929e387096b6cea41","tid":674384,"uid":37218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:38:20.000Z","msg":"英國《天空體育》報道，由於德甲慕遜加柏對利物浦小將保士達感到興趣，且不斷尋求希望得到他的加盟，紅軍最終取消了兩支球隊之間的友賽安排。<br />\n<br />\n報道指利物浦方面亦已經正式去信慕遜加柏，警告他們追求保士達的不當行為。利物浦原定在8月7日於晏菲路友賽慕遜加柏，暫時未知這場友賽取消後，利物浦會否安排另一個對手頂替。<br />\n英格蘭U17去年在印度贏得世少盃，保士達因為成為賽事神射手，一時鋒頭無兩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180520/58215153\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180520%2F58215153&d=%2B0s%2FEaa309fbeZiZdSkjvwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=13a5a634\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180520%2F58215153&h=a8b1f40d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180520/58215153</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.tribalfootball.com/articles/fuming-liverpool-pulled-out-of-gladbach-friendly-over-rhian-brewster-row-4232410?utm_source%3Dmediafed%26utm_medium%3Drss-feed%26utm_campaign%3DFeed-Latest%2BArticles%2Bfor%2BLiverpool\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribalfootball.com%2Farticles%2Ffuming-liverpool-pulled-out-of-gladbach-friendly-over-rhian-brewster-row-4232410%3Futm_source%253Dmediafed%2526utm_medium%253Drss-feed%2526utm_campaign%253DFeed-Latest%252BArticles%252Bfor%252BLiverpool&d=%2B0s%2FEaa309fbeZiZdSkjvwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=5d8a3154\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tribalfootball.com/articles/fuming-liverpool-pulled-out-of-gladbach-friendly-over-rhian-brewster-row-4232410?utm_source%3Dmediafed%26utm_medium%3Drss-feed%26utm_campaign%3DFeed-Latest%2BArticles%2Bfor%2BLiverpool</a><br />\n<br />\n有無人發現愈來愈多德甲隊吼實英超幼幼?"},{"pid":"c9651f7c5c6d7affa28dbb4d021c1eaa5c8b4650","tid":674384,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:49:35.000Z","msg":"梗係買英撚幻幻啦，養到成隻義和碑咁都有英格蘭球隊接貨，養得勁嘅話就曼市雙雄用錢掟死你，點都唔會豬"},{"pid":"20ab39080031d9242028a00b05bb9f0c77e565de","tid":674384,"uid":37218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9651f7c5c6d7affa28dbb4d021c1eaa5c8b4650","tid":674384,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:49:35.000Z","msg":"梗係買英撚幻幻啦，養到成隻義和碑咁都有英格蘭球隊接貨，養得勁嘅話就曼市雙雄用錢掟死你，點都唔會豬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:52:23.000Z","msg":"近一年加柏、RB、多蒙特都買過英撚幼幼，睇嚟德甲慢慢會愈買愈多英人<br />\n同埋如果德甲賣返走嘅話，個價錢對英超球隊嚟講應該都係濕濕碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}